title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Apr 8 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Apr 8 2022
description:
Disney CEO grovels to the woke mob. Clay says what used to always be the quintessential, middle America, pro-America, kid-driven Disney "has lost their minds with this woke agenda." New Jersey to teach gender identity to 2nd graders, justifying Florida bill. Disney producer says she identifies as "biromantic asexual." C&B both admit to having "no earthly idea" what that is. Psaki: Biden backs "gender-affirming health care" for kids. Shouldn't we wait until at least 18 years old before having sex change surgery? Buck says it's "reckless" if doctors go along because they are afraid of losing their licenses. Democrat Senator Chris Murphy says "Trump wing" of GOP is at war with transgender kids.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
